<DOCNO> LA070290-0073 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 241863 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 2, 1990, Monday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
