Weaver ; Photo, David Edson ; Photo, Paul George ; Photo, Ray Ybarra ; Photo, 
Deborah Selby ; Photo, Kevin Gertsman ; Photo, Rob Tobias ; Photo, Sonya 
Hawkins ; Photo, Floyd Bates 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
