Photo, Imelda Marcos greets supporters outside the federal courthouse in New 
York City after a jury found her not guilty on all charges. Reuters; Photo, 
Adnan Khashoggi smiles at reporters following court verdict. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
