<P>
THE SIDELINES; 
</P>
<P>
RYAN NO-HITS CLUBHOUSE THIEVES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
DALLAS 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fenway Park burglars, as have so many Fenway Park would-be hitters, struck out 
against Nolan Ryan. 
</P>
<P>
Burglars broke into the home and visitor clubhouses over the weekend and made 
off with several game jerseys, but got nothing from Ryan. 
</P>
<P>
The Texas Rangers realize how highly sought Ryan memorabilia is among souvenir 
collectors, so the club takes special security precautions to protect the 
pitcher's personal possessions. 
</P>
</TEXT>
