<P>
JACK TYGETT; JOYCE SCHUMAKER 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
738 words 
</P>
